mkdep 2.3 Release 20 december 2004

  8. Replace insecure string copy functions with strlcat/strlcpy. 
  7. Expand buffer space for file names to 1024 characters.
  6. force LC_ALL=C before calling cpp, to avoid problem with localized
     strings in cpp output parser.
  5. sprintf() -> snprintf() conversion.

